org.perfcake.message.sender

Class CamelSender

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.perfcake.message.sender.AbstractSender
      • org.perfcake.message.sender.CamelSender
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MessageSender

    public class CamelSender
extends AbstractSender
    Sends requests to a Camel endpoint which extends the variety of protocols PerfCake can support. Do not forget to add Camel components on the classpath (in ext directory).
    Author:
    Martin Večeřa
